msgid "Return to Heart of the Elders, Part 2"
msgstr "重返久远腹地，第二章"

msgid "Scenario V–B: Return to Heart of the Elders, Part 2"
msgstr "冒险V–B：重返久远腹地，第二章"

msgid "Search the collection for the new Harbinger of Valusia <i>(The Sleeper Returns)</i> and set it aside, out of play. If the Harbinger of Valusia would enter play during this scenario, use this version instead of the original one."
msgstr "搜索收藏，找出新版的瓦卢西亚的预示者<i>(沉睡者归来)</i>并将其放在一边，位于场外。如果在本冒险期间，瓦卢西亚的预示者将要入场，不使用原版，改为使用其新版。"

msgid "Create the exploration deck. This is done by taking the 5 remaining single-sided locations from the <i>K’n-yan</i> encounter set. Include only 1 of the 2 locations with each of the following connection symbols, chosen at random."
msgstr "构建探索牌堆。拿取<i>昆扬</i>遭遇组剩余的5张单面地点，对于以下每个连接符号的地点，只随机加入2个地点中的1个。"

msgid "Remove the other 4 [[Ancient]] locations from the game. Do not include any of the other encounter cards listed in the original setup instructions. (There should be a total of 5 cards, not counting the set-aside Descent to Yoth.)"
msgstr "将其他4个[[古代]]地点从游戏中移除，不要查看。不要加入原版的冒险设置指示中列出的其他遭遇卡。(卡牌总数应为5张，不算入放在一边的深入幽嘶。)"

msgid "The 'check your supplies' ability on the Mouth of K'n-yan can be used from any location, and it discards enemies as well as treacheries."
msgstr "昆扬之口的‘查看你的补给品’能力可以在任意地点使用，且该能力除了丢弃诡计之外还会丢弃敌人。"

msgid "Which investigator should add the \"Sticky Goop\" to their supplies?"
msgstr "要在哪位调查员的补给品中记录“黏液团”？"

msgid "Found \"Sticky Goop\""
msgstr "找到“黏液团”"

msgid "Sticky Goop"
msgstr "黏液团"

msgid "A mysterious scepter you found in a subterranean swamp."
msgstr "你在地下沼泽找到的神秘权杖。"

msgid "A sticky goop you found in a subterranean swamp."
msgstr "你在地下沼泽找到的黏液团。"
